  <data name="Winget_Description" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Software sharaxaadda sawirka shaashada ee Windows iyo Linux.

Sifooyinka:
- **Fallaarooyinka** - Si xoogga ugu jiid meelaha gaarka ah oo leh fallaarooyinka la hagaajin karo
- **Sharaxaadaha** - Ku dar sharaxaadaha qaabka xaanshida oo leh qoraalka la tifatiri karo
- **Xusuusimaha** - Samee sanduuqyada qoraalka oo leh macluumaad dheeraad ah
- **Muujeynta xadka** - Muuji meelaha oo leh mustatilyo xad leh
- **Dhiirinta** - Qari macluumaadka xasaasiga ah oo leh saameynta dhiirrinta
- **Qalab doorashada** - Dooro qaybo sawirka si aad u koobiyayso (Ctrl+C) ama tirtirayso (furaha Delete)
- **Goynta toosan iyo dhererka** - Goyn meelaha toosan ama dhererka ee sawirka
- **Muujinta** - Muuji meelaha xiisaha leh
- **Maareynta mashruuca** - Keydsiga tooska ah ee mashruuca iyo muuqaalka yar-yar
- **Wadaagida barnaamijka** - Ku shaqeeya Windows iyo Linux labadaba</value>
  </data>
